data.description: H&B due by Thur, Jan 25th at noon.  This is a must see! 3 bedrooms, 1 full bath ranch with family room addition. Updated kitchen and bath. Beautifully clean and move in ready. Great for entertaining or spending quality time with family and friends. Kitchen has lots of space for cooking together and plenty of room for a dining table, with SS appliances and an abundance of storage. Open to the family room with a wood burning fire place, breakfast bar and sliding doors that open to a patio and large fenced in back yard. Ample size bedrooms and a large bathroom that includes a soaking tub, will complete your main floor living. Basement is partially finished with a large entertainment area and a large bonus room for an office or workout room. Plumbed for an extra bath. 2 car detached garage!
